name: Attuned_Mark_of_Supremacy_C
display_help: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character. Enhances the accuracy of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Accuracy.Scale}% and damage by {Boost.Attrib.Damage.Scale}% . This enhancement can only be slotted in a Mastermind pet power.
